Package: bootLong
Type: Package
Title: The Block Bootstrap Method for Longitudinal Microbiome Data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pratheepa Jeganathan
Maintainer: Pratheepa Jeganathan <pjeganat@stanford.edu>
Description: bootLong provides a set of tools for differential abundance analysis and subsampling method to compute the optimal block size for the block bootstrap method of longitudinal microbiome data.It also provides a set of tools to visulaize the correlogram, lag-plot, and variogram of longitudinal microbiome data. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
